<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
		<title>邀请有奖</title>
	    <style type="text/css">
	    	.invitationGift_wrap{
	    		width: 18.75rem;
				height: 30.45rem;
				background-image: url(/images/app/user/invitationGift_bg.png);
				-webkit-background-size: cover;
				-moz-background-size: cover;
				-ms-background-size: cover;
				background-size: cover;
	    	}
	    	.invitationGift_footer_wrap{
	    		position: fixed;
	    		left: 0;
	    		bottom: 0;
	    		width: 100%;
	    		height: 6.0rem;
	    		background-color: rgba(0,0,0,.9);
	    		font-size: 0.6rem;
	    		-webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
				box-sizing: border-box;
	    	}
	    	.invitationGift_footer{
	    		position: relative;
	    		width: 17.5rem;
	    		height: 5.0rem;
	    		margin: 0 auto;
	    		padding-top: 0.5rem;
	    	}
	    	.invitationGift_text img{
	    		width: 2.5rem;
	    		height: 2.5rem;
	    		margin-right: 0.7rem;
	    	}
	    	.invitationGift_text p{
	    		width: 14.2rem;
	    		text-align: Justify;
				text-justify: inter-ideograph;
	    		color: #fff;
	    	}
	    	.invitationGift_btn{
	    		width: 100%;
	    		position: absolute;
	    		bottom: 0;
	    		left: 0;
	    		height: 1.75rem;
	    		line-height: 1.75rem;
	    	}
	    </style>
    </head>
    <body>
    	<input type="hidden" id="recommendCode" name="recommendCode" value="$!{recommendCode}">
    	<div class="invitationGift_wrap">
    		<div class="invitationGift_footer_wrap">
	    		<div class="invitationGift_footer">
	    			<div class="invitationGift_text clearfix">
	    				<img class="fl" src="$!{avatar}">
	    				<p class="fl">亲，您的好友<span>$!{userName}</span>邀你来51返呗购物省钱，请注册的时候填写推荐人的ID<span class="fsc_orange">$!{recommendCode}</span>，立即开启省钱之旅</p>
	    			</div>
	    			<div class="bgc_orange bdr_4 tac fsc_f invitationGift_btn">马上注册拿返利</div>
	    		</div>
    		</div>
    	</div>
    	<script type="text/javascript">
    		var recommendCode = $("#recommendCode").val();
    		$(".invitationGift_btn").click(function(event) {
    			window.location.href = "/app/user/register?recommendCode="+recommendCode;
    		});
    	</script>
    </body>
</html>